    "burn_cap": {
      "source_index": 3,
      "index": 3,
      "doc": " Burn (delete) a capability\n\n This permanently revokes the capability.\n After burning:\n - No one can decrypt memories for this context\n - Object is permanently deleted\n\n @param cap: The capability to burn (consumed)",
